{"tid":890309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【健康上網?】 騰訊明年起全線遊戲產品將啟用健康系統","createTime":"2018-11-05T08:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T01:06:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5efba53390a4db2ffcd94d224b8f722a0c1d14e9","tid":890309,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T08:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20181105/s00010/d67712779dab5f3c0f1280c8c693b676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20181105%2Fs00010%2Fd67712779dab5f3c0f1280c8c693b676.jpg&h=19071221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n騰訊（0700）公布，截至目前，旗下遊戲《王者榮耀》健康系統已經穩定運行並順利升級，即將完成全體用戶強制公安實名校驗。為了保護未成年人健康上網，騰訊將把這項經實際驗證有效的防沉迷措施作為標準配置，在全線遊戲產品中啟用。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊指，去年《王者榮耀》遊戲中率先啟用了健康系統，計劃今年內為自主研發和代理發行在內的9款熱門移動遊戲完成健康系統的接入和啟用，明年起健康系統的覆蓋範圍將擴大至其他移動遊戲和PC遊戲產品。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊稱，凡是啟用健康系統的遊戲產品，其用戶賬號都會接受強制的公安實名校驗。校驗通過後，未成年人的帳號將納入健康系統進行防沉迷，12歲或以下人士每天限玩1小時，12歲以上未成年人每天限玩2小時。校驗未通過的賬號將禁止登錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1541394153507&amp;issue=20181105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1541394153507%26issue%3D20181105&d=wM3bPP5psT4qZB%2BIA%2FDayqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=90e3a3b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1541394153507%26issue%3D20181105&h=efc0ce7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1541394153507&amp;issue=20181105</a>"},{"pid":"a7ee3d737228643e35ea5d2335d3ffd565089df8","tid":890309,"uid":214776,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T08:23:31.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜柒都要實名<br />\n玩幾耐都關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小朋友放假打下機2個鐘好過份咩<img src=\"/ass